---
title: Awaiter lifecycle
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: Awaiter::new()
    Idle --> Waiting: AwaiterSet::register()
    Waiting --> Waiting: AwaiterSet::register() (updates waker)
    Waiting --> Notified: AwaiterSet::notify_one()
    Waiting --> Idle: AwaiterSet::unregister()
    Notified --> Idle: Awaiter::take_notification()
